    \textbf{Attribute} & \textbf{Description}\\
    \hline
     ID bin & bin code\\
     \hline
     ID Garbage Collector & personal and unique code of Garbage Collector\\
    \hline
     Date of creation & expressed in m/dd/yy h:min\\
     \hline
